text: Adrienn Nyeste (born 14 December 1978) is a Hungarian gymnast. She competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics and the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Hungary Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:People from Békés County
